Set Recipe Notifications: Get notified when your scheduled recipe runs.
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.
To set a recipe notification: Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows or Edit Dataset Recipes. Click the triangle to select Notification. In the Notify Me About picklist, select warnings, failures, or all events. To receive a notification when the run takes longer than the specified time, select Elapsed time notification, and then select hours and minutes.
